I move to amend HB1393
Page 2 Section 1 Lines 3-4
Of the Engrossed Bill
By deleting after the word "instruction" and before the semicolon ";" the
following language: "based on alternate academic achievement standards"
And by inserting after the word "instruction" and before the semicolon ";"
the following language: "that will be assessed by alternate achievement
standards that promote access to and progress in the general education
curriculum".
